WEBVTT

00:14:28.560 --> 00:14:30.440
Why would you ever want to do that?

00:14:32.320 --> 00:14:33.576
Well, I'll tell you why.

00:14:33.600 --> 00:14:35.320
Because this is the ultimate selfie.

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:37.800
(Laughter)

00:14:38.440 --> 00:14:41.000
This is taken from six billion miles away,

00:14:42.040 --> 00:14:43.240
and that's Earth.

00:14:44.800 --> 00:14:46.000
And that's all of us.

00:14:47.240 --> 00:14:50.760
And if that little thing goes,
all of humanity goes.

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:54.536
And the reason you want
to alter the human body

00:14:54.560 --> 00:14:57.336
is because you eventually
want a picture that says,

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:59.296
that's us, and that's us,

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:00.736
and that's us,